                       MOVE    MCP-WIDGET(2:2)     TO  PIN9
                       PERFORM 410111-PIN-SET-SEC
                   ELSE
                       EVALUATE    MCP-WIDGET
                           WHEN    "BSH"
                               PERFORM 410112-SHIFT-SEC
      *----(01.00.01) LINE ADD START ----------------------------------
